page.title: 20Changing Schools
page.content: At the end of this year I will be going to Healing school.It is very big comprared to this school.I am quite nervous about going up.It will seem strange being the youngest instead of the oldest.We have been to look round the school for a morning.Some of the kids looked massive compared to us.The school is quite nice.It has a lot of rooms for different subjects like maths,English,science etc.I have been to a fairly big schhol before but for the people that haven't it wiil be quite a big shock.On our morning looking round we saw all the classrooms.We did a bit of music and had a go on the computers.We also ate lunch.I am quite looking forward to going.
